OL,3,CVan driver cleared of 'road rage'
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FA van driver has been cleared of
OL,7,Fmurder after his vehicle struck
OL,8,Fanother motorist following a "road
OL,9,Frage" row.
OL,11,FPaul Bowles, 50, was pronounced dead
OL,12,Fat the scene of the collision in
OL,13,FOldham, Greater Manchester, just after
OL,14,F7pm Wednesday on 26 March.
OL,16,FShortly before, Andrew Robson, 33, and
OL,17,FMr Bowles got out of their vehicles as
OL,18,Fthey pulled up to the Elk Mill
OL,19,Froundabout traffic lights in
OL,20,FChadderton.
