OL,6,FProsecutors said Robson returned to
OL,7,Fhis van after blows were exchanged and
OL,8,Fthen intentionally swerved left into
OL,9,Fthe path of Mr Bowles, who was knocked
OL,10,Fto the ground.
OL,12,FRobson said the collision was an
OL,13,Faccident, adding he did not see Mr
OL,14,FBowles or realise he had collided with
OL,15,Fhim as he drove off.
