OL,6,FJurors at Manchester Minshull Street
OL,7,FCrown Court also found Robson not
OL,8,Fguilty of an alternative count of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter in which the defendant
OL,10,Fwas accused of intending to cause some
OL,11,Fharm, but short of "really serious
OL,12,Fharm".
OL,14,FIn his closing speech, defence
OL,15,Fbarrister Simon Csoka KC reminded the
OL,16,Fjury of the evidence of the
OL,17,Fprosecution's road collision expert,
OL,18,Fwhich said tyre marks at the scene
OL,19,Fwere consistent with "torque steer".
