OL,6,FHe said such an unintentional pull to
OL,7,Fthe side due to too much acceleration
OL,8,Fwas a "classic accident".
OL,10,FGordon Cole KC, prosecuting, said it
OL,11,Fwas the Crown's case that Robson "lost
OL,12,Fhis temper" and intended to inflict,
OL,13,Fat least, really serious harm to Mr
OL,14,FBowles.
